This dataset was obtained from the OpenfMRI project (http://www.openfmri.org).
Accession #: ds007
Description: Stop-signal task with spoken & manual responses

Please cite the following references if you use these data:

Xue, G., Aron, A.R., Poldrack, R.A. (2008). Common neural substrates for inhibition of spoken and manual responses. Cereb Cortex, 18(8):1923-32. doi: 10.1093/cercor/bhm220


Release history:
10/06/2011: initial release
3/21/2013: Updated release with QA information
2/17/2016: Updated with corrected orientation in NIFTI headers, includes masks and brain extractions.
           New orientation information was extracted from original dicom files using dcm2niix.

